quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,Yallay dudda le fayla-le isi naqasu Nabii Mucammadal izza Qhuraan kitab oobiseeh cakkik makot tanim kee ittawway kay addal ma-hanna
  18,2,"Yalli ama kitab massah yan kitab kaa abe koros gibdi digaalay kay xaquk obtak edde meesiisamkeh, kaadu moominiiniy meqe taamoomi abbaasitta diggah meqe galto (jannat kinnuk) loonumul ken aytikumusamkeh"
  18,3,Usun Ama jannatih niqmatih addat umman waarak
  18,4,Kaadu korosuy Yalli baxa haysite itte kaat meesiisamkeh
  18,5,"Usun Yallal haanamak hebeltoh ixxiga maloonuuy ken abbobti mali, ken afittek tawqe Qangara (Yalli baxa haysite iyyaanam kinnuk) manxu nabaah qaxumaa usun iyyaanam malon dirab maxco akke waytek"
  18,6,"Nabiyow atu isi nafsi hammii kee rookah qiddam faxxa usun derre kot cabeeniik lakal, ama Qhuraanal aamine weenim kee Yalli xalay-le iyyaanamih maxcoh faxe waytii kee Rookak gexxaamah"
  18,7,"Nanu diggah baaxô bagul eneyyi ittam baaxoh bila abneeh teetil yan marah tuxxiq abne, meqe taamah keenik yayse maraa kee uma taamah keenik gaca mara keenik mokkorraah naaxigemkeh"
  18,8,kaadu diggah nanu baaxô bagul bilak eneyyi ittam addunya gaba kalta waqdi burtay (baaxo kinnuk) cooxuk tu-elle aneewayta tet abna
  18,9,Wonna hinnak Nabiyow gablâ maraa kee ken migooqa elle tunkuttube luc Ni-astootik cagalah dibuk cakkumuh (Qajabah) tan astay lafitak raqta makka-lin qaranwaa kee baaxô gino wohuk cakkumuh lafitak raqtak
  18,10,"Nabiyow keenih cus: teemene furrayna, ken mari diinik ken korsaamih meesih gablâ fanah kelitteeh tet orben waqdi, tokkel:Ni -Rabbow ku-xaquk nacrur neh acuyaay iimaanal diggi nee hayis, kaadu ni-caagid neh xabbacoysaay massa-le gital tirri nee hayis iyyen"
  18,11,"Tokkel gablah addal kaxxa xiiniy aytiita xongolo keenik edde aabbe wayya hayta keenil qidne, maggo liggidittey ixxi kak yimixxige edde sugen"
  18,12,Tohuk lakat woo xiinik ken ugusneh namma buttak A-furrayna gablal waktik sugteh gideh ixxigat keenik yayse mara naaxaguh